race.comment: HUSSON'S REVENGE (6) was out of the money two runs back then again missed the frame last start when he settled well back over 1100m at Gatton, beaten 3 lengths into eighth. Has the talent to take this out. IT'SALLSAIDANDONE (3) went fast early when scored by 2 lengths last time out over 1315m at Coffs Harbour. Should enjoy a good run just off the speed. Suitably placed so anticipating another big run. MA'S EPIC (1) found the line nicely to grab second last time out over 1315m at Coffs Harbour. Likely to feature. INVISIBLE TARGET (5) was below his best last time, finishing 11th and beaten 10 lengths over 1350m at Doomben. Can atone in this weaker contest.
